Giffords, who represented Arizona, was critically wounded in 2011 by a gunman in a Tucson, Ariz., shooting that left six people dead.. Dated: 10.02.2012. data.text: Former U.S. Rep. Gabrielle Giffords, left, and her husband, Mark Kelly, congratulate ships sponsor Roxanna Green at a ceremony to announce the U.S. Navys naming of the newest littoral combat ship, USS Gabrielle Giffords (LCS 10), Feb. 10, 2012, at the Pentagon. Giffords, who represented Arizona, was critically wounded in 2011 by a gunman in a Tucson, Ariz., shooting that left six people dead.
